 sing target mez.  With corpses laying around in a tight dungeon, it makes it hard to target.  Here is what I have found useful.<br>
<br>
Press F-9 for an overhead view.  It makes targeting a bit easier.  When you target your first mob, start the song.  Then immediately target your next mob, and right after the song takes hold of the first mob, start the song again.  If there is athird mob, do the same thing again.<br>
